# CDN Complete Developer Network

## Overview

This project is a RESTful API for managing a directory of freelancers. It includes user registration, authentication, and role-based access control.

## Technologies Used

- ASP.NET Core 8
- Entity Framework Core
- SQL Server
- JWT Authentication
- PasswordHasher for password hashing

## Endpoints

- `POST /api/auth/signup` - Register a new user and return a JWT token
- `POST /api/auth/signin` - Authenticate a user and return a JWT token
- `GET /api/users` - Get list of users
- `GET /api/users/users/{id}` - Get list of users by user id
- `PUT /api/users` - Update a user (Admin only)
- `DELETE /api/users/{id}` - Delete a user (Admin only)
